INNER JOIN [USUARIO_PROYECTO] AS [u] ON [p].[ID] = [u].[ID_PROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [u].[IDSEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [s].[ID_CUENTA] = [c].[ID]

INNER JOIN [RECURSO] AS [r] ON [u0].[ID_RECURSO] = [r].[ID]
WHERE ([p].[ID] = @__id_0) AND ([r].[NOMBRE_RECURSO] = 'Socio')
